### 1) Login to Supabase
# @name login
POST {{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password
apikey: {{supabaseAnonKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}"
}

### 2) Protected route without token -> expect 401
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/profile/me

### 3) Protected route with valid token -> expect 200
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.access_token}}

### 4) github analyze with worker
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/github-analysis/trigger
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "githubUsername": "yassine-krichen"
}